### Defense in Depth Layers with Citations:

| Layer | Control | Citation to Finding | Effort | Trade-off |
|-------|---------|---------------------|--------|-----------|
| **Identity** | MFA + Jump Host | C2 traffic from 10.1.30.101 | M | User friction |
| **Perimeter** | Egress/DNS filtering | DNS to exczx.com succeeded | S | May block legit domains |
| **Segmentation** | Micro-segmentation | Direct outbound from internal server | M | Management complexity |
| **Application** | TLS inspection | Encrypted TLSv1.2 C2 traffic | M | 5-10% performance hit |
| **Data** | DLP + Encryption | 6.8MB exfiltration at 4-5 seconds | L | $50K+ annually |
| **Observability** | NSM + SIEM | 6,498 packets to C2 generated no alerts | M | Staff training required |
| **Response** | SOAR automation | 72-hour response window in brief | L | False positive risk |

### Expected Outcomes After Hardening:

| Threat | Before | After | Mitigation |
|--------|--------|-------|------------|
| C2 beaconing | Successful (6,498 packets) | BLOCKED | Egress filter + DNS block |
| Data exfiltration | 6.8MB exfiltrated | BLOCKED | DLP + TLS inspection |
| IP discovery | icanhazip.com reached | BLOCKED | Egress allow-list |
| Malicious downloads | .txt files downloaded | BLOCKED | DNS filtering |
| Lateral movement | Possible | BLOCKED | Micro-segmentation |

